}], "answer": "b", "explanation": "Yes! The answer is \"I like pencils, pens, and markers.\"."}, {"type": "explain", "title": "You've got this!", "body": "Great work learning about Commas in a Series! Now tap a worksheet to practice and earn points. You can always come back to this lesson."}]$tl$::jsonb
